HEADWORD: Slumming
<hw>Slum"ming</hw>, <pos>vb. n.</pos> <def>Visiting slums. Sometimes
used humorously, in reference to the appearance of a dignified person in
a situation generally thought of as low-class.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

